 <H1>Recursion Semantics (contï¿½d)</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>Pro: a simple header states the limit of the action
</H2>
</UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Con: it is very difficult to specify the recursion behavior of all functions
</H2>
</UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Recommended solution: move the specification of the Depth header and recursion semantics to a separate specification
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>allows the main specification to continue without being held back by quibbling over definition of recursion semantics
